name: Sponsored Orphans
query:
select full_name,gender,nationality_orphan,date_of_birth_orphan,place_of_birth_orphan,tabSponsorship.start_date,tabSponsorship.end_date
from tabOrphan 
join tabSponsorship on tabSponsorship.orphan = tabOrphan.name 
where tabOrphan.gender = %(gender)s 
and tabSponsorship.start_date <= %(date_on)s
and %(date_on)s <= tabSponsorship.end_date
